## Phase 1 — Database & Scripture Foundation (Days 3–6)

### TASK-005 · Prisma Setup & Database Connection

**Files**
- `server/prisma/schema.prisma`
- `server/src/config/db.js`
- `server/src/config/env.js` (minor update)

**Steps**
1. `npm install @prisma/client && npx prisma init`
2. Write full schema (User, Scripture, DailyMessage, Conversation — see implementation plan)
3. `npx prisma migrate dev --name init`
4. `db.js` — exports singleton PrismaClient
5. On `GET /health`, include a DB ping

**Acceptance Criteria**
- [ ] `npx prisma migrate dev` completes without errors
- [ ] `npx prisma studio` shows all 4 tables with correct columns
- [ ] `GET /health` returns `{ status: "ok", db: "connected" }`

