- `server/tests/aiService.test.js`

**Steps**
1. `npm install @google/generative-ai`
2. `gemini.js` — initialises `GoogleGenerativeAI` with key rotation support (round-robin over multiple keys if provided)
3. `aiService.js` — wraps `generateContent`, adds retry (3x, exponential backoff on 429/503)
