## Phase 6 — Polish, Beta & Launch (Days 35–42)

### TASK-027 · Rate Limiting & Security Hardening

**Files**
- `server/src/middleware/rateLimiter.js`
- `server/src/app.js` (update)

**Rules**
- `/api/auth/send-otp`: max 3 requests per phone per 10 minutes
- `/webhook/whatsapp`: no limit (Twilio is trusted source — use signature auth)
- `/api/*`: max 60 requests per IP per minute

**Steps**
1. `npm install express-rate-limit`
2. Create named limiters for OTP and general API
3. Apply to routes in `app.js`

**Acceptance Criteria**
- [ ] 4th OTP request within 10 min → 429 `{ error: "Too many requests" }`
- [ ] 61st API request per minute → 429
- [ ] Webhook is not rate-limited (Twilio sends cluster of messages)

---

### TASK-028 · Error Monitoring & Logging

**Files**
- `server/src/utils/logger.js`
- `server/src/middleware/errorHandler.js` (update)

**Steps**
1. `npm install winston`
2. `logger.js` — structured JSON logger (info, warn, error levels); writes to console + optional file
3. Replace all `console.log` calls with `logger.info/warn/error`
4. Error handler: log full stack trace via logger; return sanitised message to client

**Acceptance Criteria**
- [ ] All info logs are JSON format with `timestamp`, `level`, `message`
- [ ] Errors include stack trace in log but only a safe message in HTTP response
- [ ] `logger.warn("test")` appears in Railway logs

---

### TASK-029 · End-to-End Test Checklist

**Files**
- `scripts/e2e-checklist.md`

**Manual test scenarios (run before beta)**

| # | Scenario | Expected |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | New number sends "Hi" | Onboarding step 0 starts |
| 2 | Complete full onboarding | User in DB with `isOnboarded=true` |
| 3 | Set deliveryTime to +2 min | Message arrives on WhatsApp |
| 4 | Reply to daily message | Streak increments, reply saved |
| 5 | Skip 2 days | Streak resets to 0 |
| 6 | 7-day streak | Milestone message sent |
| 7 | Send "What is karma?" | AI replies with Gita reference |
| 8 | Web login with OTP | JWT stored, redirect to dashboard |
| 9 | Dashboard shows streak | Matches DB value |
| 10 | Change rashi in settings | Next daily message uses new rashi |

**Acceptance Criteria**
- [ ] All 10 scenarios pass before beta launch
- [ ] Zero unhandled promise rejections in Railway logs during 30-minute stress test

